Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.59,0:03:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}終於來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.96,0:03:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}日本向新基地送出物資的同時
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.27,0:03:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}通過DROMLAN 也給我們送來了這些補充物資
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.07,0:03:44.88,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}※DROMLAN\N\h{\fscx80\fscy80}毛德皇后地航空網路項目，是由南極洲東部建立基地的11個國家簽署的，借用兩個考察站{\r}\N\h{\fscx80\fscy80}（挪威特羅爾站、俄羅斯新拉扎列夫站）的長距離冰跑道，作為國際飛機中轉站的合作交通協議。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.15,0:03:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們的資材就算齊全了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.01,0:03:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要今年立刻搭建起觀星天文台 還是天方夜譚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.51,0:03:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不過只要有心堅持 花上幾年時間估計…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.93,0:03:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們得去那邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.23,0:04:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}至少所有人都是這麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.23,0:04:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但那是貴子斷絕音信的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.74,0:04:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}絕對會有危險
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.12,0:04:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}該怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.43,0:04:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是糟透了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.21,0:04:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}老媽肯定把照片傳遍SNS了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.78,0:04:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不也很好嗎 這樣還能宣傳我們的轉播呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.92,0:04:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}日向？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.41,0:04:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊…我的也麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.94,0:04:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}賀年卡只寫給店長一個人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.72,0:04:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}剛才那幾個朋友不用了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.42,0:04:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊 雖說是賀年卡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.70,0:04:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也要等到船回到日本後才能送到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.20,0:04:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我去一下廁所
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.42,0:04:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.65,0:04:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.82,0:04:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她在生氣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.42,0:04:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有那麼痛啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.08,0:04:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她是不是在緊張啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.29,0:04:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}報瀨也要去上嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.99,0:05:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}開什麼玩笑 開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.75,0:05:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}開什麼玩笑！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.87,0:05:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}開什麼玩笑！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.80,0:05:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.26,0:05:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}放晴了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.72,0:05:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以可以帶我們參與海冰和地質的調查了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.72,0:05:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我會準備攝影機的 你要想好怎麼報導
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.28,0:05:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊 嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.44,0:05:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}探險探險
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.80,0:05:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你說要做報導的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.27,0:05:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我可不管你等一下情不情願啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.41,0:06:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}日向 就是剛才…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.72,0:06:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}剛才只是測試 所以不算欠你的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.28,0:06:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.70,0:06:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快點 馬上就要出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.24,0:06:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這就來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.39,0:06:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}三年前就一起做過了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.61,0:06:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}誰叫貴子前輩什麼都想做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.73,0:06:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.87,0:06:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊 她到處跑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.06,0:06:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}報瀨 你媽媽還來過這裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.42,0:06:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.73,0:06:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.75,0:06:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把那個拿來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.72,0:06:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.04,0:06:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這下面都是冰塊 所以要用蒸汽熱個洞出來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.01,0:06:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還有 我們去的應該是倫灣角吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.01,0:06:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fs30\pos(830,650)\clip(726,610,936,660)}（Rundvågshetta）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.35,0:06:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這名字聽起來就好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.81,0:06:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那是個岩石裸露的地區
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.41,0:06:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是你找信惠 她可能願意帶你過去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.21,0:06:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我要去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.41,0:06:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這裡是海冰組
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.72,0:06:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}地質組的信惠小姐聽得到嗎 請回話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.01,0:07:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}聯繫不上 聖誕之後
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.53,0:07:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大前年收到的石榴石…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.14,0:07:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}乾燥的岩石 和乾涸的愛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.15,0:07:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}收不到郵件 冷淡的阿優
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.00,0:07:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}現在無法聯絡 請回話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.61,0:07:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.67,0:07:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對啊 這溫差好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.86,0:07:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別弄我了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.21,0:07:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你們看 好壯觀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.95,0:07:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}南極好壯觀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.28,0:07:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}從這個角度看很有趣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.17,0:07:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}天空在眼前流淌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.44,0:07:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不知道能不能看到極光
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.96,0:08:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要到晚上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.61,0:08:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我們在的這段時間 不會有夜晚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.64,0:08:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}日向
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.97,0:08:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你有沒有什麼煩心事？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.91,0:08:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}煩心事？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.55,0:08:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}應該是那個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.82,0:08:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}空氣太乾燥 嘴唇都乾巴巴的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.26,0:08:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}護唇膏也凍得硬邦邦的 很難塗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.73,0:08:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我懂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.88,0:08:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}的確很難受 感覺都要脫皮了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.44,0:08:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.55,0:08:27.79,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}乾巴巴的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.67,0:08:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}戶外隊員請立刻回到基地中央區
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.52,0:08:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}或是到有應急食品的建築內避難
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.06,0:08:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}完全沒改善
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.09,0:08:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你還是放棄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.35,0:08:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}話說報瀨人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.92,0:08:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}剛才有人問她會不會打麻將
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.94,0:08:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的假的 她會嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.54,0:08:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}感覺很有趣 我也在她背後觀摩了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.60,0:08:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人字旁加個五讀作什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.60,0:08:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}伍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.49,0:08:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}準備好的白板正好湊一對呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.20,0:08:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是準備好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.41,0:09:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那個鳥好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.48,0:09:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「滾出去！」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.32,0:09:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好過分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.67,0:09:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是說嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.63,0:09:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不就問她幾句嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.47,0:09:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}報瀨本來就心胸狹隘嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.39,0:09:13.42,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康儷中黑\bord0\b0\an5\fs30\1c&H767876&\frx328\fry14\pos(998,114)\frz333.8}封鎖名單
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.39,0:09:13.42,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an5\fn華康儷中黑\bord0\fs40\1c&H7262CA&\frz333.5\frx328\fry2\pos(522,482)}刪除
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.39,0:09:13.42,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an5\fn華康儷中黑\bord0\fs40\1c&HAD9981&\pos(450,618)\frz331\frx340\fry4}解除封鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.51,0:09:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.13,0:09:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}胡了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.69,0:09:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}門清混一色 雙南風 寶牌3 16000點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.15,0:09:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的假的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.10,0:09:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你不會小時候就跟貴子一起圍著牌桌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.18,0:09:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是的 偶爾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.33,0:09:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不玩了不玩了 不可能贏的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.12,0:09:33.14,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康中特圓體\bord0\fsp35\fs150\1c&H3725E9&\t(0,2500,0\fs70)\move(384,4,534,42,33,2619)}麻將帝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.88,0:09:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對手竟然是吟和貴子的女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.59,0:09:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}三宅在這嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.33,0:09:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大概在洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.72,0:09:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.84,0:09:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她朋友發了封電郵到基地來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.22,0:09:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}朋友？
