Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.47,0:10:32.21,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\fn華康儷中黑\bord0\fs80\1c&H48404A&\b0\be1\t(0,1740,0\fs45)\move(114,482,330,448,36,1704)}對不起三宅同學 讓你這麼孤單
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.65,0:10:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}報瀨？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.46,0:10:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.86,0:10:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}日向？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.51,0:10:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.57,0:10:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一點而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.38,0:10:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是寄給日向的郵件吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.58,0:10:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你就這樣擅自打開來看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.17,0:10:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為…因為我很擔心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.86,0:10:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為你一個人不知道在生什麼氣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.55,0:10:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是卻什麼都不說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.31,0:10:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你生氣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.69,0:11:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}原來你看到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.20,0:11:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好好把話說清楚啊 不然我會擔心的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.96,0:11:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怕你是不是隱瞞了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.48,0:11:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怕你是不是有什麼話說不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.30,0:11:14.09,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an5\fn華康儷中黑\bord0\fs60\1vc(&HEFCABA&,&H60513F&,&HEFCABA&,&H60513F&)\b0\be2\rnd5\frz341.6\frx28\fry344\pos(392.666,476.667)}對不起三宅同學 讓你這麼孤單
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.55,0:11:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}醜話說在前頭 這可不是什麼好事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.38,0:11:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我本來不想提 你們聽了也不會好受
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.77,0:11:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}夠了 快點說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.01,0:11:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}簡單來說 就是我退出社團的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.54,0:11:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}既然是大會 絕對是讓跑得快的上場啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.91,0:11:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}跟什麼年級的無關啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.01,0:11:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是高三的學姐這次大賽後就要引退了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.12,0:11:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為這種原因放水 才是對她們不敬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.99,0:11:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}200公尺 三宅日向
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.36,0:12:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.69,0:12:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你們沒跟那個笨蛋說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.28,0:12:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}說了啊 都叫她看看臉色了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.18,0:12:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那一瞬間 我覺得什麼都無所謂了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.63,0:12:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那怎麼可能 明明都是她們的錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.21,0:12:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人真的很可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.63,0:12:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她們就是明白這一點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.05,0:12:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}才想盡辦法把錯推到我頭上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.64,0:12:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等我退隊 還亂傳我的閒話和謠言
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.32,0:12:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}難道這就是你退學的原因嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.47,0:12:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}日向
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.52,0:12:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抱歉我就是條喪家犬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.73,0:12:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那發信過來的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.17,0:12:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 那時候的隊友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.90,0:12:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}說想在轉播時跟我說幾句話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.20,0:12:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她們說朋友能去南極 自己也很驕傲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.44,0:13:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我才想到「呵呵 我們原來是朋友啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.62,0:13:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}感覺如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.89,0:13:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼？和你們的想像有出入？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.71,0:13:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}感覺這裡都不像是地球了 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.02,0:13:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哎？啊…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.73,0:13:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好神奇的顏色
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.80,0:13:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們去對面搭帳篷和設置天線
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.12,0:13:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.38,0:13:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你要糾結到什麼時候啊 快忘了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.71,0:13:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你這樣害我都覺得不舒服了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.15,0:13:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.96,0:13:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你覺得我為什麼要來南極？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.63,0:13:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為這裡一無所有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.82,0:13:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想和無拘無束的人們去一無所有的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.59,0:13:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你們看 景色這麼漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.58,0:13:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}冰 地層 雪水
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.74,0:13:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}每一個都是不曾看過的顏色和形狀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.38,0:13:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒有任何我們知道的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.08,0:14:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這裡有著和以往完全不一樣的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.13,0:14:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我是為了享受這一切才來的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.74,0:14:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你們這樣不就浪費了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.16,0:14:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我知道了 那就把它忘掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.83,0:14:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}先去紮營 紮營
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.37,0:14:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這可不是在玩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.60,0:14:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}報瀨？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.95,0:14:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}才沒有浪費
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.24,0:14:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}肯定不會浪費這一切的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.24,0:14:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}跟科幻電影一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.50,0:14:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要不要喝點水看看 很好喝哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.02,0:14:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能喝嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.53,0:14:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}某種意義上而言 可能是全世界最乾淨的水了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.85,0:14:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}幾乎沒有被人觸碰過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.11,0:14:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}氣溫也沒有高到能讓細菌繁殖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.38,0:14:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我是第一個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.71,0:14:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好狡猾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.24,0:14:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.42,0:14:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.52,0:14:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.70,0:15:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的耶 冰冰涼涼的好好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.17,0:15:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}滋潤身心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.42,0:15:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}報瀨要喝看看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.98,0:15:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等等再說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.05,0:15:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}聯繫上了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.95,0:15:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}說句話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.42,0:15:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.86,0:15:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.78,0:15:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這裡是倫灣角的小淵澤 請回話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.77,0:15:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好 這裡是昭和 信號良好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.79,0:15:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}景色如何 請回話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.01,0:15:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 感覺像是被蛋糕包圍了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.15,0:15:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蛋糕？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.78,0:15:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}貴子也說過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.30,0:15:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抵達的那一刻喊說「想吃巧克力蛋糕！」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.22,0:15:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}媽媽也……
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.01,0:15:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}最棒的天然水了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.15,0:15:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.68,0:15:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.43,0:15:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}做得真好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.45,0:15:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小理很擅長些怪工作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.97,0:15:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一點也不奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.22,0:16:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能從衛星上看到這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.55,0:16:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 這是給拍衛星照等特殊情況定位用的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.88,0:16:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}會非常清晰的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.18,0:16:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}現在沒在拍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.33,0:16:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}阿優
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.07,0:16:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}阿優
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.95,0:16:17.33,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那個 我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.33,0:16:20.11,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不用管她 她每次都這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.55,0:16:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這種地方都有標記 肯定有人在看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.12,0:16:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我可沒話中有話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.36,0:16:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這就是極樂了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.59,0:16:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為溫度越來越低了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.81,0:16:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還有更厲害的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.32,0:16:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.81,0:16:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等下一鍋水滾了 就做煎蛋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.42,0:16:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你真的很喜歡煎蛋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.69,0:16:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在新加坡吃早餐時 也吃了好多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.51,0:17:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}日向
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.49,0:17:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我去打水 你陪我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.73,0:17:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不夠用嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.49,0:17:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對不起 是我用掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.14,0:17:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小理
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.12,0:17:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}風吹起來真的超冷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.43,0:17:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那我也會有點想死呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.37,0:17:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想了很久
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.55,0:17:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果跟日向有同樣的遭遇會怎麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.48,0:17:31.50,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an5\fn華康儷中黑\bord0\fs60\1vc(&HEFCABA&,&H60513F&,&HEFCABA&,&H60513F&)\b0\be2\rnd5\frz341.6\frx28\fry344\pos(392.666,476.667)}對不起三宅同學 讓你這麼孤單
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.90,0:17:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}遭遇了這麼過分的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.67,0:17:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但某天 又若無其事地聯絡自己
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.28,0:17:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為她們所犯下無可挽回的錯而道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.68,0:17:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.82,0:17:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不可能保持平靜 不可能笑得出來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.23,0:17:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}報瀨又不是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.12,0:17:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就算是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.50,0:17:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就算是這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.30,0:17:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}報瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.41,0:17:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把手套撿起來 給我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.65,0:18:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只要手就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.12,0:18:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}報瀨老管閒事真是煩人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.16,0:18:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.13,0:18:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對不起 我可能還是挺害怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.11,0:18:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}日向…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.35,0:18:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我好怕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.06,0:18:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.60,0:18:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我說了 只要手就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.48,0:18:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}謝謝你帶我一起來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.90,0:18:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}煎蛋做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.05,0:18:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好 這就來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.79,0:18:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.55,0:18:52.08,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康儷中黑\bord0\fs30\1c&H778285&\pos(904,84)\frz344.9\frx348\fry16}可選的過年蕎麥麵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.55,0:18:52.08,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康儷中黑\bord0\fs30\1c&H778285&\frx348\fry16\pos(908,202)\frz349.1}加天婦羅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.55,0:18:52.08,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康儷中黑\bord0\fs30\1c&H778285&\frx348\fry16\pos(928,296)\frz353.3}加年糕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.55,0:18:52.08,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康儷中黑\bord0\fs30\1c&H585A5A&\frx348\fry16\frz353.3\pos(912,368)}純蕎麥麵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.27,0:18:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}切得真爛 這是刀削麵啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.92,0:18:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}夠細了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.27,0:18:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}重桿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.03,0:18:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}從桿麵開始啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.60,0:18:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}10分鐘後就正式來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.83,0:19:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.19,0:19:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}結果曬痕還是沒消
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.37,0:19:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這說明你在南極玩得很嗨呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.09,0:19:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.77,0:19:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是原諒她們 會輕鬆些嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.61,0:19:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你想原諒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.89,0:19:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果原諒了能輕鬆點就好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.79,0:19:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但想像道完歉 她們鬆了一口氣的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.78,0:19:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就一肚子火呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.70,0:19:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「真他媽的」？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.50,0:19:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.54,0:19:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我的肚量也夠小的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.91,0:19:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這裡是上午9點 和日本有6個小時的時差
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.77,0:19:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}正式開始前 我能說一句嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.25,0:19:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}報瀨？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.74,0:19:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不好意思 你們能別纏著三宅日向了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.81,0:19:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}報瀨？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.23,0:19:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都是因為你們 日向才退學 飽受艱辛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.85,0:19:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你們可能覺得她恨你們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.94,0:20:06.70,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}深夜零時の地平線　広がる世界は
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.70,0:20:11.04,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}今日がずっと眩しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.24,0:20:21.74,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}鼻の奥がツンとした　きれいできれいで
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.74,0:20:26.27,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}胸が痛くなるほどに
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.02,0:20:35.94,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}両手いっぱいありったけの人に
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.13,0:20:46.71,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}意味なんかないって言われ続けたとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.71,0:20:59.29,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}宇宙(そら)から届くひかり　逆さまの星空見上げて
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.29,0:21:03.15,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}ここから始めよう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.15,0:21:11.73,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}さあ　迷いなんて置き去りにして
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.73,0:21:18.15,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}探しに行くんだ　見果てぬ世界を
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.15,0:21:26.22,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}勇気出して　進んでいこう
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.94,0:20:06.70,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}眼前是深夜零點的地平線 一片廣大的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.70,0:20:11.04,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}今天一直是那麼耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.24,0:20:21.74,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}我激動得鼻尖一癢 眼前的景象是那麼美麗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.74,0:20:26.27,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}燦爛到叫我心口作痛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.02,0:20:35.94,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}許許多多的人 裝滿雙手也擠不下的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.13,0:20:46.71,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}都在勸我不要白費力氣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.71,0:20:59.29,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}只是仰頭看見那顛倒的星空 灑下的星光
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.29,0:21:03.15,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}我會從這裡揚帆啟航
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.15,0:21:11.73,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}把心裡的迷茫留在岸邊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.73,0:21:18.15,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}去探索廣闊無垠 斑斕神秘的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.15,0:21:26.22,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}只要拿出勇氣 走出大大的一步
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.44,0:20:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可能覺得她每天會想起田徑隊而掉眼淚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.68,0:20:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.43,0:20:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但那是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.86,0:20:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}日向現在和我們過得極其開心而充實
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.52,0:20:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}享受著你們留在日本絕對體驗不到的旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.04,0:20:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}日向已經積極地邁出了腳步
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.27,0:20:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}和我們一同邁開了腳步
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.69,0:20:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}報瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.19,0:20:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}多棒啊 這才是友情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.52,0:20:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我跟日向不一樣 個性很差
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.87,0:20:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就直說了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.10,0:20:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你們就懷著這份不安的心情活下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.16,0:20:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你們傷害別人 帶給別人痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.43,0:20:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就背負著過錯活下去！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.59,0:20:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這就是傷人的代價
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.42,0:20:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這就是傷害我朋友的代價！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.19,0:20:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}報瀨…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.98,0:21:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}事到如今還想求個心安？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.81,0:21:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別開玩笑了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.93,0:21:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}開始準備吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.51,0:21:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.64,0:21:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今年很快就要結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.78,0:21:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有電視看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.57,0:21:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}雖然是去年的錄影
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.57,0:21:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.57,0:21:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}阿優！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.77,0:21:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}阿優 阿優！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.20,0:21:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們也來撞掉煩惱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.49,0:21:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.35,0:21:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}用這個嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.65,0:21:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}全都撞掉吧 日向
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.25,0:21:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}說不定會撞壞哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.66,0:21:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一個鐵桶而已 無所謂的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.47,0:21:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.83,0:21:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那第一下四個人一起來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.63,0:22:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}1 2！
Comment: 0,0:22:03.04,0:22:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,ED-FF FINAL
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.20,0:22:23.89,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}長いトンネルの出口を探していた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.27,0:22:34.81,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}かすかな光の匂いがしてる方へ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.18,0:22:40.43,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}間違っても　笑えるさ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.43,0:22:51.38,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}ここから始めよう　僕は旅に出よう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.59,0:23:02.13,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}汚れた真ん丸のビー玉　握りしめて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.29,0:23:13.40,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}言えなかった言葉も　きっと見つかるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.56,0:23:19.02,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}バカにされたって構わない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.02,0:23:24.35,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}信じてゆこう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.20,0:22:23.89,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}尋找著漫長隧道的出口
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.27,0:22:34.81,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}向著泛著微光氣味的方向前進
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.18,0:22:40.43,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}就算走錯了 也別忘了微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.43,0:22:51.38,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}從這裡開始 我將踏上旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.59,0:23:02.13,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}緊緊捏住手心裡 髒髒的玻璃珠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.29,0:23:13.40,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}沒說出口的話 我也一定會找到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.56,0:23:19.02,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}隨你們嘲笑吧 我不在乎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.02,0:23:24.35,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}要相信自己 邁出腳步
